Amon the Wolf was a noble
Baatezu in the service of Geryon, the commander of 40
companies of Osyluth. He resembled a large human with the head
of a wolf, and had a winter wolf servant.
Amon was exiled with Geryon. He presently wanders Avernus as one of the "rabble of devilkin" there.
Sources: A Paladin in Hell, Monster Manual II (1E), Fiendish Codex II